{"tid":2349301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"GD元旦更新IG「五隻手握一起」發文引淚崩！預告BIGBANG回歸？","createTime":"2021-01-01T12:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-01T18:52:25.000Z","uid":16659,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c6429370c364c6270746264a593f439c0c1264dc","tid":2349301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:35:58.000Z","msg":"迎接2021年，不少藝人在社群網站上拜年，G-Dragon也不意外，他1月1日深夜在IG發文，其中一張黑白照片，是5隻手交疊接連握著彼此的手腕，而粉絲對這張照片相當熟悉，就是BIGBANG五人4年前發行最後一張團體專輯留下的照片，讓不少粉絲看完流下熱淚！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5371/d5371649.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5371%2Fd5371649.jpg&h=75d61309&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GD元旦更新IG。（圖／翻攝自GD IG、BIGBANG臉書）<br />\n<br />\nGD在IG上發布兩張照片，一張是截圖手機桌布，時間就落在2021年1月1日的1點11分，桌布背景是他自己戴著口罩，最近沉醉於畫畫的他，連桌布背景都相當有藝術氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n另外一張則是黑白照，五隻手握著下一人的手腕，串成一個星狀，是BIGBANG在2015年宣傳《MADE》系列專輯，他們拍攝MV時手繪刺青的造型，GD也曾於2016年分享在自己公開的IG上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5371/e5371650.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5371%2Fe5371650.jpg&h=c419c789&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲GD發出「BIGBANG五隻手握一起」引粉絲淚崩。（圖／翻攝自GD IG）<br />\n<br />\n由於成員勝利因為捲入性交易、賭博等相關醜聞而於2019年宣布退出演藝圈，BIGBAN實質上已成為4人組合，YG娛樂官網的BIGBANG團體照也不再有勝利。然而GD發出的圖片，讓不少粉絲看了直呼，「BIGBANG永遠是5人」、「這張照片是新年最好的禮物」、「看到都要哭了，GD覺得BIGBANG是5人」！<br />\n<br />\n也有媒體猜測這是否預告了BIGBANG在今年即將回歸，目前全員退伍的他們，日前曾傳出GD已經在為回歸作準備，已開始著手製作新歌，讓粉絲相當關注他們的下一步動向。"},{"pid":"d7b91e69d115a2ce4994169aa2670d248b7477fd","tid":2349301,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:36:15.000Z","msg":"哭𠹌咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a67e07368b6b549ef4e40492beb09dcd989849f4","tid":2349301,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"龍哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34aeaba39fc14f48b8ffc6105d43b42268e065fe","tid":2349301,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a67e07368b6b549ef4e40492beb09dcd989849f4","tid":2349301,"uid":229026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:36:32.000Z","msg":"龍哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:39:55.000Z","msg":"bang bang bang<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0050f865900afabae79279d35cc84913065dfa","tid":2349301,"uid":58630,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:40:06.000Z","msg":"啲手整哂啲黑色野上去 又五又一 gd係咪犯左法<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e0cc3746a0f99767bd16bae229848cc0fdd53c","tid":2349301,"uid":10290,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-01T12:40:50.000Z","msg":"五大訴求缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/a